<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause"?><clause id="_12b722ba-4631-4f0a-937d-1ef1b5acc8db" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>F2P3</sptc><title id="_18ea9585-4208-46b3-8dae-e140025412c7">Prevention of surface water accumulation</title><archive-num>2019: SA FP1.8</archive-num><subclause id="_52ae864b-4a41-4ccb-b534-f3165cb4dcbd" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_1b773253-5e40-435e-9c5c-03c90ced830c">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>In laundries, bathrooms or rooms containing shower facilities the floors must be installed in a manner that will prevent accumulation of surface water which could create unhealthy or hazardous conditions.</p></subclause></clause>